{
  "stem": "11882.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, they thought Hitler's too smart for that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because everyone had the view stupidity to start a war, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But Hitler was a very limited man in his knowledge of geography.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I think-- some of my students too, they had no training in geography.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If I'd say, well, New York is as far away from Hamburg as San Francisco is far away from New York as New York is from Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They didn't believe that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They didn't think I'd learned-- learned it right in school, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "For them, America was a funny little country, over there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My students, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And for Adolf, apparently, also.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I told Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Sachs as we walked around the Alster.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was still trying to lose weight, and I didn't mind getting some exercise.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was a Sunday afternoon, and he was going up to pick little Annamarie up and bring her back home, and the-- and the governess.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he took-- we took this walk, and he said, well, he said, I-- I worry if I think there might be a war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I had listened with him on January 30 to Hitler's speech a few months-- six, seven, eight months before, when Hitler said, but if there is war, all the Jews of Europe will be wiped out.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that he didn't like the sound of, that was very clear.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he was beginning to believe these things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There was enough suffering.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He suffered enough in Herschberg with the people afraid to say hello to him on the street and his little daughter cringing if he wanted her to go for a walk with him, you know.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he said, I thought there was a war coming.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I said, oh, I really think that's just bluff.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
